{"tid":2182500,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"政府公布今個財政年度首4個月錄得赤字1837億港元","createTime":"2020-08-31T10:32:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-31T11:06:08.000Z","uid":339805,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"35d6962f663d752c09a8f162534a2060b74254d0","tid":2182500,"uid":339805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T10:32:37.000Z","msg":"政府公布，本港今個財政年度首4個月錄得赤字1837億港元，主要是薪俸稅及利得稅等主要收入，大多在財政年度後期收取，以及就「現金發放計劃」及「防疫抗疫基金」下各個項目的付款所致。<br />\n期內，整體開支2898億元，收入1061億元。<br />\n<br />\n至7月底，財政儲備9766億元。<br />\n<br />\n#香港電台 #政府 #財政儲備 #赤字<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/RTHKVNEWS/photos/a.723529797755079/3788247764616585/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FRTHKVNEWS%2Fphotos%2Fa.723529797755079%2F3788247764616585%2F&d=2%2FmELneL9Q%2Bp6j2sEUyr0yq0XD4M5CHb8byFtBYuAsM%3D&h=87d8829a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/RTHKVNEWS/photos/a.723529797755079/3788247764616585/</a>"},{"pid":"1bb2dd1838bb5f469351c4cbe438147fb3704c43","tid":2182500,"uid":191926,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T10:35:15.000Z","msg":"希望埋單3500億-4000億<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1986fe44a5fde4e6ef0ee28e03161e3ae775fef7","tid":2182500,"uid":188176,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T10:36:20.000Z","msg":"叫有錢佬比多d稅囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e827f269b59689144e1d9f9da35e6d8f4adde94","tid":2182500,"uid":366165,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T10:36:38.000Z","msg":"沒事兒沒事兒，仲有9700幾億起人工島<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"701b3cc4999c441c1bcef71311a31cbe1876d52f","tid":2182500,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T10:38:31.000Z","